title: Data Saturday Brisbane 2026
abstract:
SSW is sponsoring Data Saturday #79 - Brisbane 2026!!

About the event: It is an event run by volunteers from the data community & SQL community for the community. 

Our event will strive to offer content across Microsoft Azure Technologies. This community event offers content across Data Management and Administration, Cloud and Hybrid Architecture, Analytics, Business Intelligence, Artificial Intelligence, DevOps, Application Development and more.

See more:
https://datasaturdays.com/Event/20260228-datasaturday0079#venue
